Magnetar Capital Partners LP: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback


























magnetar capital partners lp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Magnetar Capital Partners LLC operates as a private equity firm. The Company focuses on management buy-outs, acquisitions, mergers, recapitalizations, restructuring, and other corporate situations. Magnetar Capital Partners serves clients worldwide.




Corporate Information
Address:

1603 Orrington Avenue
13th Floor
Evanston, IL 60201
United States


Phone:
1-847-905-4400


Fax:
-


Web url:
www.magnetar.com























