ShareOverviewMagnetar Financial, LLC is a registered investment advisory firm located in Evanston, Illinois. The firm manages 91 accounts totaling an estimated $19,895,021,418 USD in assets under management. Its operations include 258 employees and is categorized as providing investment advisory services to 100 clients. Many more details can be found below. You can also click here to see a list of all 29 investment advisors located in Evanston, Illinois.
